{"tid":1458844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣建議] 機場文宣請多用英文！英文！英文！","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:00:19.000Z","uid":34475,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c949cf345600eed732fa828bf727e1e48eb3023d","tid":1458844,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"揀得機場其中一個原因應該係想俾國際同外國遊知道發生咩事<br />\n今日見到有好多巴絲都好好，會叫英文口號，亦有英文勁既會主動同遊客解釋發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過機場大部分文宣印刷都係中文，相信去得機場大家都知道發生左咩事，所以唔需要太多中文宣傳（當然保留d黎表達意見立場都係岩既)<br />\n個人小小見解，覺得最好整多d英文文宣，同埋文字最好簡潔d，等外國遊客立下眼都知大概咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後，多謝各位文宣組既爆肝努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"75b0d2aa0ebc8ab144462b310ce76eb6a11fdad5","tid":1458844,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64acb95a4441a92604773a9b37fc5767025d8e45","tid":1458844,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96f4178795b50e8bff7938eafc644194159f357","tid":1458844,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd787cb8264e4b7c1d193c3cfe17a8ee903559a","tid":1458844,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5e68a9c555507e1c0f15b913bd64490ec1f3f6","tid":1458844,"uid":249015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"都唔知